# Heroicon Utility Class System

This project includes a comprehensive Heroicon utility class system in [src/css/foundation/icons.css](mdc:src/css/foundation/icons.css).

## Available Icon Classes

### 24px Solid Icons (Default)
```css
.heroicon.heroicon-[iconname]
```
- 318 icons available
- Default size when using base `.heroicon` class

### 24px Outline Icons
```css
.heroicon.heroicon-outline-[iconname]
```
- 318 icons available
- Outline versions of the icon set

### 20px Solid Icons
```css
.heroicon.heroicon-20.heroicon-[iconname]
```
- 318 icons available
- Compound selector for 20px sizing

### 16px Solid Icons
```css
.heroicon.heroicon-16.heroicon-[iconname]
```
- 275 icons available
- Compound selector for 16px sizing

## Usage Patterns

### Basic Usage
```html
<!-- Default 24px solid -->
<div class="heroicon heroicon-user"></div>
<div class="heroicon heroicon-home"></div>

<!-- 24px outline -->
<div class="heroicon heroicon-outline-user"></div>

<!-- 20px solid -->
<div class="heroicon heroicon-20 heroicon-user"></div>

<!-- 16px solid -->
<div class="heroicon heroicon-16 heroicon-user"></div>
```

### Base Heroicon Class
Always include the base `.heroicon` class which provides:
- `display: inline-block`
- `width: var(--spacing-24)` (24px default)
- `height: var(--spacing-24)` (24px default)
- `background-size: contain`
- `background-repeat: no-repeat`
- `background-position: center`
- `flex-shrink: 0`

## Common Icon Names
Popular icons include: `user`, `home`, `chevron-down`, `chevron-up`, `chevron-left`, `chevron-right`, `x-mark`, `plus`, `minus`, `check`, `arrow-left`, `arrow-right`, `heart`, `star`, `envelope`, `phone`, `calendar`, `clock`, `cog`, `bell`, `trash`, `pencil`, `eye`, `lock-closed`, `magnifying-glass`

